g":"<blockquote>有幾奇<br />\nmk唔代表窮<br />\n車可以係老豆或者呀哥既<br />\n住豪宅都可以係租<br />\n唔好睇表面野judge人</blockquote><br />\n呃到渣大牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/192537_94ceb96b8b8861b5475b410ec205db20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F192537_94ceb96b8b8861b5475b410ec205db20.jpg&h=09072b69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5472f5bbab8db17c4846d3984b475080c5ba409c","tid":175730,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾奇<br />\nmk唔代表窮<br />\n車可以係老豆或者呀哥既<br />\n住豪宅都可以係租<br />\n唔好睇表面野judge人</blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但當你發現<br />\n現實社會係<br />\n個mk無論係<br />\n表面內裹<br />\n老豆同呀哥都真係咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就會灰左下，現實上真係大把呢種人"},{"pid":"8d52473a424abdc7b6a65ae4ab26032397b66bfe","tid":175730,"uid":49603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾奇<br />\nmk唔代表窮<br />\n車可以係老豆或者呀哥既<br />\n住豪宅都可以係租<br />\n唔好睇表面野judge人</blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但當你發現<br />\n現實社會係<br />\n個mk無論係<br />\n表面內裹<br />\n老豆同呀哥都真係咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就會灰左下，現實上真係大把呢種人</blockquote><br />\n又唔洗灰喎<br />\nmk同有冇錢係冇關係的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有米mk 應該叫二世祖<br />\n因為mk多數都係出身自窮人家庭"},{"pid":"ae3a4f7e8e649438edce685fe9b4e95a61dc8146","tid":175730,"uid":49603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾奇<br />\nmk唔代表窮<br />\n車可以係老豆或者呀哥既<br />\n住豪宅都可以係租<br />\n唔好睇表面野judge人</blockquote><br />\n呃到渣大牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/192537_94ceb96b8b8861b5475b410ec205db20.jpg\" da